name: Siobhan Guthrie
what_you_do: Siobhan Guthrie is the Founder of KinesiologyZone, an organization that provides training and education in Systematic Kinesiology.
who_you_serve: People who seek a better life for themselves, first by improving their health and then being inspired to help others, such as family, friends and their community.
signature_programs: The Academy of Systematic Kinesiology (TASK) in Ireland, Balanced Health Course
business_focus: Providing excellent training in Systematic Kinesiology to help people improve their health and inspire them to help others.
